    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earths Edge </strong>is a cooperative first-person shooter where you and up to three of friends pilot Mechs (<strong>EM-BR Units) </strong>into battle for control over a new ore that has changed the course of the world. Face two enemy factions, each  with their own soldiers and mechanized units. The ore has corrupted someone or something  nearby, posing an unpredictable threat for everyone trying to gather it.     <br>   <br><strong>Key Features:  </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/b4f1500fc64c88c71ef125b28e8eae3d.avif?t=1769625381\" width=1560 height=64 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/fd431169816b404917137c281834358e.poster.avif?t=1769625381\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/fd431169816b404917137c281834358e.webm?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/fd431169816b404917137c281834358e.mp4?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cooperative :</strong> Play alone or join forces with 3 other pilots (1-4 Players). Combine your skills and abilities to  complete mission objectives.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/8bcaefb77d65bfe58a3286e1b03f3aa4.avif?t=1769625381\" width=1560 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/cd9b5c97454b88b08e86725c671a9824.poster.avif?t=1769625381\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/cd9b5c97454b88b08e86725c671a9824.webm?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/cd9b5c97454b88b08e86725c671a9824.mp4?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Momentum-based movement: wall-running, sliding and double jumps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/a319565fd97490a105662acc381b1247.avif?t=1769625381\" width=1560 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/ad9553113bc4d9d0998f4a087df52858.poster.avif?t=1769625381\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/ad9553113bc4d9d0998f4a087df52858.webm?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/ad9553113bc4d9d0998f4a087df52858.mp4?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mech Combat:</strong> Call down your Mech (EM-BR Unit)and drop into the fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the mech’s heavy arsenal and firepower to eradicate enemy forces.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/ab199ff91e56df6b4ecb7f8f333e5be5.avif?t=1769625381\" width=1560 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/80ac1ebd3b60338cadeb22f1cf102444.poster.avif?t=1769625381\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/80ac1ebd3b60338cadeb22f1cf102444.webm?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/80ac1ebd3b60338cadeb22f1cf102444.mp4?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destruction:</strong> A lot of things are destructible in Earths Edge, and some paths can only be accessed by the Mechs (EM-BR Units). Keep your eyes peeled!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/24a1f9f54caf87ddd4688470d3af6b69.avif?t=1769625381\" width=1560 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/ec7bf8c4f34068e76df1c96f316fbb6b.poster.avif?t=1769625381\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/ec7bf8c4f34068e76df1c96f316fbb6b.webm?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074980/extras/ec7bf8c4f34068e76df1c96f316fbb6b.mp4?t=1769625381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mech Customization:</strong> Upgrade and customize your Mech (EM-BR Unit) with a variety of weapons, armor and abilities to suit your style and create your very own mech. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Other Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enemy Factions:</strong> Engage in battles against two factions, each with unique weapons and mechanized units.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover the World's Unknown History:</strong> Uncover the secrets behind the corrupted foes, and the newly found ore that changed the Earth &quot;Lunom&quot;. Can u discover what lies on Earths Edge ?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pilot Customization:</strong> Upgrade and customize your Pilot (Scorcher) and their weapons to suit your style. Choose from a variety of weapons, attachments, abilities and skins.</p></li></ul>",
